title: No. 7 Tech downs No. 11 Virginia, 5-2, during Clash opener - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 7 Tech downs No. 11 Virginia, 5-2, during Clash opener  VT hokiesports.com
description: Scoring on each of its four extra-base hits on Friday night, the No. 7 Virginia Tech baseball team earned a statement, series-opening victory at No. 11 Virginia as the Hokies downed the Cavaliers, 5-2, at Davenport Field at Disharoon Park.
